{
  "stem": "3804.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because he had to understand the Jews, to know their language, their mentality, and all these kind of thing, not because-- it's only for one reason, how that he will kill them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They will send them to the concentration camp with-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "With no question.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he used a lot-- how do you say?-- the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because, you know, it's like Kastner-- Kastner in Hungary, other people, you know, to-- he understood that he has to make kind of relation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There would be no resistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the new kind of murderer, that behind a desk he could do much more, in any case, and [INAUDIBLE] weapon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first time that through-- under his desk, he sent so many Ukraines, and manipulate so many things and-- and-- and succeeded in-- in concentrate so many people, six million of Jews and maybe another six million of other people, in the concentration or killing and all this kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think even more for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For him, he-- he saw that his job is the most important thing, that he has to make it, fulfill it to the end, because this was the order of his boss, of-- of Hitler and Himmler and later Kaltenbrunner and the others.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was the job that he has to do, and he was kind of-- to show that he fulfilled as much as possible, he fulfilled his job.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did what he can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the guy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For him, Hitler was God and, in order, was the most important-- his bible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And no question about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe people ask me, what did you learn about it?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
